{"tid":631443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋輪候絕望真相：18歲申請等32年始上樓","createTime":"2018-04-16T12:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T12:57:06.000Z","uid":173617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f98ed0826f434650a4d945ed98691082db016f8d","tid":631443,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"社區組織協會代表昨日(15日)在商台節目中指出，非長者單身人士需要輪候26年，才可獲編公屋，惟按現時公屋計分及配額制規定，實際輪候時間或許更長！<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》參考房委會現行的公屋配額及計分制，以現時單身人士獲分配市區公屋至少要438分計算，若申請人於18歲開始申請公屋，直至50歲才可獲444分，即苦候32年才可「達標」入住市區公屋，倘申請者為公屋戶子女，輪候時間要更漫長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/178377/%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E8%BC%AA%E5%80%99%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8-18%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%AD%8932%E5%B9%B4%E5%A7%8B%E4%B8%8A%E6%A8%93-%E6%9F%AF%E5%89%B5%E7%9B%9B-%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%80%E6%AD%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F178377%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E7%25B5%2595%25E6%259C%259B%25E7%259C%259F%25E7%259B%25B8-18%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E7%25AD%258932%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A7%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25A8%2593-%25E6%259F%25AF%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%259B%259B-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%2580%25E6%25AD%258C&d=E8tS2js63dwapHgAhqzVQpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=800e33fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/178377/%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E8%BC%AA%E5%80%99%E7%B5%95%E6%9C%9B%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8-18%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%AD%8932%E5%B9%B4%E5%A7%8B%E4%B8%8A%E6%A8%93-%E6%9F%AF%E5%89%B5%E7%9B%9B-%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%80%E6%AD%8C</a>"},{"pid":"70cc9d25edecefcdc2d6f639242d3c2f46f90ac2","tid":631443,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"成世人人工唔過12000,先有資格<img src=\"/assets/faces/